lines.text: my life locked in a trunk
when it hurt way too much
i needed a reason to live
some love inside me to give
i had to keep on searching
i've been too sad to speak
the devil cut off my wings
i've been hurt by my past
in my dreams and it lasts
i wake up i'm not sure
i wanted to find the light
i wanna be myself but does
see god in the trees makes me
my heart so rigid i keep
with the tears that i cry...

paragraphs.text: i've been high i've been low i've been fast i've been slow i've had nowhere to go missed the bus missed the show
i've been down on my luck i've felt like giving up my life locked in a trunk when it hurt way too much
i needed a reason to live some love inside me to give i couldn't rest i had to keep on searching
te busque debajo de las piedras y no te encontre en la manana fria y en la noche te busque hasta enloquecer
pero tu llegaste a mi vida como una luz sanando las heridas de mi corazon haciendome sentir vivo otra vez
i've been too sad to speak and too tired to eat been too lonely to sing the devil cut off my wings i've been hurt by my past but i feel the future
